From 4051911dc6781c272681304e79750db9ac32c076 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Kevin Kreiser <kevinkreiser@gmail.com>
Date: Tue, 23 Jun 2026 21:31:33 -0400
Subject: [PATCH] input: touchscreen: add ChipOne ICNL9922C TDDI driver (KONKR
 Pocket FIT)

Vendored from github.com/kevinkreiser/chipone_tddi @ ad4e075, reworked for an in-tree build. CFG_CTS_WRAP_X flips touch X for the 90-degree-mounted panel.
